\mt1 1 TIMOTI  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Wun Pol wun. Kan nyaang…®t wunay…® p…®l…®wutaa kwiya. Jisas Kraist waa nyaang…®t mbut…®ga nyan wun. Godnagwi Jisaso wun kat yiga ambuk wamb…®t maa wan apma nyaang…®t mbut…®gowun. God n…®n kat kwunatnd…®. Kraist Jisas yaiga nandinya kat yelav…®ka l…®gan…®n.  
\v 2 Kan pas Timoti kat p…®l…®wut…®gowun. Jisasna mbaapma wuleimangat wuna nyan vla l…®gam…®n. M…®n kat tamba kandi kwutaa kaliwun. N…®na nyaek Godnogwi n…®na njambwi nyan Kraist Jisaso m…®n kat woviyaguga l…®ga s…®ka l…®meya vat kwimbangat wowun.   
\s1 KAVLE NYAANG∆óT NGAMBUL∆óNJA VAK KWAGALAGIYAN∆óN  
\p
\v 3 Masedonia wal…®nja n…®ma k…®pma yivat t…®ga m…®n kat wowun. Efesas wal…®nja ngepmamba al…® m…®la wowun m…®n kat. Kan ngepmamba l…®ga n…®mba kat mand…®t kavle nyaang…®t s…®mogwingwa vat kwagala ngwula waa n…®mamba awamba ndi kat.  
\v 4 Apma nyaang…®tna angwa wupmat yil…®njan ndina nyaek awat kwutaa yeta kavle vapmba ke ngambul…®ngwa waga awambam…®n ndi kat. Wungi vapmba ngambul…®njeyan God waa apma nyaang…®t ana wukiyandi. God kat wagalanjeyan nd…®nai waa apma nyaang…®t v…®s…®mogwind…® maa ndina maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®giyandi.  
\v 5 N…®n ndi kat mand…®t vapmba yet…®njangat yelav…®ka l…®gan…®n. N…®n ndi kat apma maawut yelav…®ka l…®njangat wan…®n. God kat ngwula maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®njangat wan…®n. Wungi vapmba yet…®njeyannat n…®mba kat kwunaka woviyaguga l…®giyandi.  
\v 6 Ndina nat n…®mba wan apma nyaang…®t kwaglalaa kwo nyaang…®tmba ngambul…®ga yet…®l…®gandi.  
\v 7 God tamba wand…®, p…®l…®wutnja nyaang…®k s…®mogwivat wan n…®mba wal…®gandi. Mbutnja nyaang…®t ndina maawut ana yelav…®t…®gandi. Maawut yelav…®tapman n…®mamba kwundi m…®na ngambul…®gandi.  
\v 8-10 God waa lona nj…®vwa k…®ngwiyan. K…®ta nyan God waa lo kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat mbutndeyan wovuna. God kwiya lo ndina nda. Tamba v…®ga l…®gan…®n. Apma vat yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat God ana nd…®na lo kwind…®. God kat kai waa kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat nd…®na lo God kwind…®. Nd…®na lo wuka yet…®vak kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba kat kwind…®. God yeta vapmba yet…®vak kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba kat wan lo kwind…®. Nyaek, ny…®me, nat n…®mba kat vatnyal…®ga n…®mba kat wan lo kwind…®. s…®kwuka yamb…®s…®k kwuka yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat kwind…®. Ndu v…®l…®l…®k kavle vat yet…®vat ngambul…®ga n…®mba kat God nd…®na lo kwind…®. Kandi kwuka kalil…®ga n…®mba kat wan lo kwind…®. Woseka wal…®ga n…®mba kat wan lo kwind…®. God waa nyaang…®k kat kai waa yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat kwind…®.  
\v 11 Wan apma nyaang…®t wuna nyaang…®t ana nd…®. Apma nyan God wun kat wan apma nyaang…®t yiga ambuk wand…® mala mbut…®gowun ngwuk kat.   
\s1 GOD POL KAT APMA VAK KWUT∆óNDA NJ∆óVWA KAT S∆óVU K∆óL∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 12 N…®na njambwi nyan Kraist Jisas wan apma nyaang…®t mbukwangat wun kat kwondu kwind…®. Jisasna mbang…® ana vali yind…® wan nj…®vwa wun kat kwivat t…®ndangat. Wuna nj…®vwa kwut…®ga nyanat t…®giyam…®n waa wun kat wand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga nd…® kat s…®vu k…®l…®gowun.  
\v 13 Tat Jisas Kraist kat kai waa yet…®la nyan wun. nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat kavle vat yila nyan wun. Nd…® kat nj…®ka kwus…®l…®ga yila nyan wun. Maawut yelav…®tapman wan kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®wun. Nd…®na mbaapmamba ana l…®wun. Ngi kat t…®ga God wun kat awat ana n…®ma vat yind…®.  
\v 14 Njambwi nyan wun kat awagapma n…®mamba apma vat yil…®nd…®. Kraist Jisas wuna maawut ngwand…®nd…® maa nd…® kat wuna mbang…® wiyo waavi laagand…®. Ngwand…®nd…® maa nat n…®mba kat kwunapmak kat woviyaguga l…®wun.  
\v 15 Kraist Jisas kavle vat yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat kwunapmak kan k…®pma yand…®. Kavle vat yiluwa vak kavle vak yiga yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat kwulat…®nd…®. Wan nyaangst apma nyaang…®tna. Awuk ngwula.  
\v 16 Manda kat God wun kat awat s…®lapman yind…®. Wun kavle nglei nyan Jisas Kraist wun kat kwunatnda vat nat n…®mba v…®laa yelav…®kiyandi. Wan kavle nglei nyan kat ana n…®ma vat yind…®. N…®n kat ana n…®ma vat yigiyand…®. N…®n kat al…®ps…®ga kwunakiyand…® waa yelav…®kiyandi. Wupma Jisas Kraistkat yelav…®tnjeyan nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat yet…®njeya vat klaigandi.  
\v 17 Wun Godna s…® katsoga waigowun. God nat nyana kwupmba ana l…®gand…®. Nd…® njambwi nglei l…®gand…®. nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vapmba l…®giyand…®. Nj…®mbla nj…®mbla n…®na kingat t…®giyand…®. Nd…® ana wundumba yigiyand…®. Nat n…®mba m…®nimba nd…® kat ana vl…®lgandi. Apma vatna.   
\s1 TIMOTI KAT NJ∆óVWA N∆óMAMBA AGWUT WAA WAND∆ó POL  
\p
\v 18 Mbambala m…®n kat wowun wuna nyan m…®n Timoti, wawa k…®ta nyaang…®t m…®n awup m…®la. Tamba God wand…®, nat n…®mba m…®n kat tat mbutndi. M…®n Godna nj…®vwa apma nj…®vwa kwukiyam…®n waa tat m…®n kat mbutndi. Mbutnja nyaang…®t yelav…®ka Godna apma nj…®vwa n…®mamba agwut.  
\v 19 Wan apma nyaang…®ik kat m…®na maawupmba yelav…®ka apma vat agwut. Nat n…®mba maawupmba yelav…®ka kwupmak kat kai walaa wan apma vat tamba kwagalandi.  
\v 20 V…®l…®l…®k pal…® kat wowun. Mb…®tna s…® Haimenias, Aleksanda. Mb…®lo ngivat kavle vat yimb…®t. Mb…®k kat waga k…®kliwun. Mb…®k kat Seten v…®ga l…®giyand…® wowun, Seten mb…®k kat kavle vat yil…®nd…®, wan yil…®mba God kat kavle nyaang…®t ngambul…®mba vak kwagalagiyamb…®t.   
\c 2  
\s1 GOD KAT WAGALANEYA VAT  
\p
\v 1 Tat m…®n kat God kat wagalamangat wowun. Nd…® kat wagalameya nat n…®mba kat t…®ga God kat wagalamba. God kat wagalameyan nd…® kat s…®vu ag…®mba. Nat n…®mba kat t…®ga aywaa God kat wagalamba.  
\v 2 King kat t…®ga wagalamba. Yet…®neya vak kat v…®laa njambwi n…®mba woviyagunjeya vak kat God kat wagalamba.  
\v 3 Wungi vapmba wagalameyan apma vatna. N…®n kat kwunakna nyan God apma vatna waa waigand…®.  
\v 4 God ndinyangu kat kwupmak wal…®gand…®. Wan apma nyaang…®t wutaa maawupmba yelav…®ka yet…®njangat wal…®ngand…® God.  
\v 5 God k…®ta l…®gand…®. Nd…®na nyan k…®ta nyan m…®na l…®gand…®. Wan nyan Godnogwi ndinyanguna n…®nd…®mba l…®gand…®. nd…®na s…® Kraist Jisas.  
\v 6 Jisas ndinyangu kat t…®ga ngaga yalaa nd…®na mbang…®mba n…®na kavle vak kat wenga kwind…®. Jisas kiya vak kat v…®laa God ndinyangukat aywaa kwunapmat wal…®gand…®. V…®l…®gan…®n. Ngi kat t…®ga mbambala Jisas ya vak kat nat n…®mba kat yiga mbut…®gan…®n.  
\v 7 T…®ga l…®ga wan nyaang…®t yiga ambuk nat n…®mba kat waa God wun kat wand…®. Juda ana ndi nat n…®mbak wan apma nyaang…®t s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun. Ndi kat s…®mogwiwun maa wan apma nyaang…®k kat ndina maawupmba yelav…®ka kwuta l…®mbandi walaa mbukwun.   
\p
\v 8 Ngepma ngepmamba l…®ga n…®mba kat wowun. God kat wagala ngwula wowun. Apma maawupmba yelavk…®a nd…® kat kawiga al…®. Ngwuk kat kwunakiyand…®. Ngwuk ke kimbuk yiga waleavat yelav…®ka nd…® kat wagala waa wowun.  
\v 9 Wun taagwa kat wowun. Ngwutna mbang…® m…®na ke n…®ma vak yelagaga. Apma waavwi kwusongwengan wovuna. Ngwutna mbang…® m…®na kwunaka wana yelav…®ka yet…®l…®ngweya. N…®ma sanyo l…®ga vand…® nda klalaa ke yelagaga.  
\v 10 Godna yelang…®mba l…®ngweyan apma nj…®vwa agwut. Godna nj…®vwa kwukngweyan ngwula mbang…® yelagangwa vand…® nda vla wan apma nj…®vwa l…®giyand…®.  
\v 11 Ngwut taagwa kiyak walea Godna nyaang…®t wuka l…®giyangwuk. Ana kwundi waigangwuk. Nyaang…®t wupmbangwuk. Nyaang…®t wutaa apma maawut yelav…®ka t…®mbangwuk.  
\v 12 Wun kai wowun. Taagwa laataa l…®vak kat ndu kat l…®lai ana nd…® v…®ga kaliga yet…®giyaa. Ngwuk taagwa ke kwundi waa. Ngwuk kiyak waa al…® waa wowun.  
\v 13 God Adam kat tak kwutnd…®. Ng…®ni Iv kat kwutnd…®. Ngi kat t…®ga taagwa nduna kwupmba l…®giyandi.  
\v 14-15 Adam Seten woseka waa vak kat ana wutnd…®. Iv wutaa maawupmba yelav…®ka kavle vat yil…®. Taagwa nyan kwutnjeyan apma vatna. God kat yelav…®ka nat n…®mba kat woviyaguga kwunaka yet…®njeya apma vat yet…®giyandi. Wun n…®ma nyan ana wun waa yelav…®ka apma vat yet…®njeyan wan vak wovuna. Wan vapmba yet…®njeyan God ndi kat kwunakiyandi.   
\c 3  
\s1 JISASN YELANG∆ó N∆óMBA KAT V∆óGA LA N∆óMBANA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 1 Kan nyaang…®t kwo wanja nyaang…®t ana nd…®. K…®ta nyan Jisasna yelang…® n…®mba kat v…®ga l…®vat wandeyan wan apma vatna.  
\v 2-3 Nat n…®mba kat v…®ga l…®giyaa nyan kat nd…® kavle nyana waa wanjeyan nd…® njambwi nyan ana l…®giyand…®. Taagwa k…®ta klal…®giya nyan m…®na wan nj…®vwa kwukiyand…®. Nj…®mbla nj…®mbla n…®ma ngu k…®ga tungwengwan yiga yet…®ligiyaa n…®mba kan nj…®vwamba ana l…®giyandi. Apma maawutno l…®ga nyan m…®na k…®ngi nj…®vwamba l…®giyand…®. Nat n…®mba kat yagwa walaa kwunaka k…®g…®nda kwil…®ga nyan m…®na k…®ngi nj…®vwamba l…®giyand…®. Nat n…®mba kat al…®ps…®ga nyaang…®t v…®s…®mogwil…®ga nyan m…®na k…®ngi nj…®vwamba l…®giyand…®. Nyingi lapman maawutno l…®ga apma nyan k…®ngi nj…®vwamba l…®giyand…®. Sanyo klavat woviyaguga l…®ga nyan k…®ngi nj…®vwamba ana l…®giyand…®.  
\v 4 Wan nyan nd…®na ngaymba l…®ga n…®mba kat yigumba v…®ga l…®giyand…®. Nd…®na nyangu kat waigand…®. Wuna nyangu wuna nyaang…®t awuk ngwula waa waigand…®. Ndi wukiyandi.  
\v 5 K…®ta nyan nd…®na ngaymba l…®ga n…®mba kat kavle savle v…®ga l…®ndeyan Godna yelang…® n…®mba kat ana apma vapmba ndi kat v…®ga l…®giyand…®.  
\v 6 Mbambala glei Jisasna yelang…® wuleia nyan v…®ga l…®giyaa nyan ana l…®giyan…®. Mbambala glei wuleia nyan v…®ga l…®ndeyan nd…® yelav…®kiyand…®. Wan apma nambuo l…®ga nyan wun waa yelav…®ka l…®giyand…®. Wungi vapmba tala Seten yelav…®ka la kavle vak vla yelav…®t…®gand…®.  
\v 7 Kwo l…®ga n…®mba v…®ga l…®giyaa nyan kat waigandi. Nd…® kan nyan apma nyana waa waigandi. Wan nyaang…®t mbutapman yindeyan ndi Setena mbaapma n…®mba nd…® kat kavle vat nj…®ka waigandi. Wungi vapmba Seten nd…® kat kavle yigiyand…®.   
\s1 JISASNA YELANG∆óMBA NJ∆óVWA KWUTAA N∆óMBANA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 8 Jisasna yelang…®mba nj…®vwa kwut…®giyaa ndi apma maawut s…®ka yelav…®ka l…®giyandi. Ndi kwundi v…®l…®l…®k ngambuga ana l…®giyandi. Ndi kwundi k…®ta nyaang…®t m…®na ngambuga l…®l…®giyandi. Ndi wundi n…®mba n…®mamba n…®ma ngu ana k…®giyandi. Sanya klavat wal…®giyaa n…®mba ana l…®giyandi.  
\v 9 Ndi wundi n…®mba God waa nyaang…®tna angwa mnaawupmba s…®ka yelav…®ka wan nyaang…®t kwutaa yet…®giyandi.  
\v 10 Wundi n…®mba wan nj…®vwa kwutnjeya vak v…®ga av…®. ndi apma vat kwukiyandi? E? Kavle vak kwukiyandi waa v…®ga av…®. Apma vat kwut…®njeyan ndi kat wan nj…®vwa agwi kwukandi.  
\v 11 Wundi n…®mbana taagwa ndinagwi apma maawut s…®ka yelav…®ka l…®giyandi. Ndi ke yi yaga kavle nyaang…®t ngambuga s…®mblan yet…®l…®njeya. Ndi n…®mamba n…®ma ngu ke k…®ga. Ndi mand…®p mand…®p ke yiga yet…®njeya.  
\v 12 Jisasna yelang…®na nj…®vwa kwupmat t…®gaiyaa nyan k…®ta lagwa klaiga nyana kwukiyaa. Nd…®na ngaymba l…®giya n…®mba nd…®na mat nyangu kat aywaa yigumba v…®ga l…®giyand…®.  
\v 13 Jisasna yelang…®na nj…®vwa k…®ta nyan kwutndeyan nat n…®mba nd…® kat v…®ga waigandi. Nd…® njambwi nyana waa waigandi. Nd…® kwonduo l…®giyaa t…®giyand…®. Kwonduo l…®ndangat t…®ga nd…®na mbang…® Kraist Jisas kat wiyo waavi taaganda vat kat vaatapman nat n…®mba kat mbut…®gand…®.   
\s1 GODNA VATNA ANGWA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 14 Wun ngwuk kat kwiyatapman yalaa v…®vat wowun ngwuk kat. Tat ngwuk kat wan nyaang…®tna ngwuk kat p…®l…®wukwa.  
\v 15 Wun kat kematnjeyan ngwuk kat p…®l…®wukwa nyaang…®t v…®ga lamba yelav…®ka l…®giyangwuk. P…®l…®wuka nyaang…®t v…®laa Godna mbaapma n…®mbonala yet…®ngweya vak kat yelav…®ka wuka l…®giyangwuk. Ngwuk Godna ngay vla l…®gangwuk. God ngwula maawupmba yet…®lgand…®. Ngay kat tawnja kwaal…®k wan ngay kat kwutaa l…®gand…®. Ngay ana ndaigand…®. Ngwuk God waa apma nyaang…®t kwutaa l…®gangwuk. Ana ndaga kavle yiga kwo vatnat t…®giyand…®. Ngwuk ngay kat tawnja kwaal…®k vla l…®gangwuk.  
\v 16 Maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa l…®na nyan nd…® njambwi nyana Kraist. N…®n kat Godna angwa vat n…®n kat s…®magal…®gand…®. Ngwuk kat mbukwun. Ndinyanguna mbang…® klalaa yand…® mala ndinyangu v…®ndi nd…® kat. Nd…®na maawut God kwiya maawupmba yelav…®ka apma vat m…®na yet…®nd…®. Ensel nd…® kat v…®laa wandi. Nd…® n…®ma nyana. Nd…® njambwi nyana waa wandi. Nat n…®mba ngepma yiga nd…®na s…® mbut…®ndi. Ngepma ngepmamba la n…®mba nd…®na s…® wutaa maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa l…®ndi. God wand…®, ny…®nangwutnat wokend…®.   
\c 4  
\s1 WOSEKA WAL∆óGA NYANGUNA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 1 Tamba Godna waagan kupma wand…®. Ng…®ni nat n…®mba wan apma nyaang…®t kwagalalaa kavle nyaang…®t woseka wal…®nja nyaang…®t wukiyandi. Seten waiga nyaang…®t wukiyandi waa wand…®.  
\v 2 Woseka wal…®ga n…®mba wan kavle nyaang…®t mbut…®gandi. Kavle maawut yelav…®ka yet…®l…®ga n…®mba wan kavle nyaang…®t mbut…®gandi. Nd…®na maawut kiya n…®mbana maawut vla l…®gand…®. Ana yigumba s…®ka l…®gand…®.  
\v 3 Ngwuk taagwa ke kla waa wal…®gandi. Nat k…®g…®nda ke k…®ngweya wal…®gandi. K…®g…®nda aywaa k…®nangat God kwutnd…®. God kat maawupmba yelav…®ka God waa nyaang…®t kwutaa l…®ga n…®mba God kat wagalaga s…®vu k…®laa k…®g…®nda aywaa k…®l…®gandi.  
\v 4 God kwukna k…®g…®nda apma k…®g…®nda m…®na l…®gand…®. Wan k…®g…®nda kat ke kai waa kwagalaga. God kat wagalaga s…®vu k…®laa k…®giyangwuk.  
\v 5 God wan apma k…®g…®nda waa wand…®. N…®n God kat wagalalaa k…®g…®nda kat s…®vu k…®laa k…®l…®gan…®n. Wumb…®k v…®l…®l…®k nda t…®mban k…®g…®nda nglaat…®gand…®.   
\p
\v 6 M…®n kat p…®l…®wukwa nyaang…®t v…®laa m…®nagwi l…®ga k…®ta mbaapma n…®mba kat mbupmeyan apma vatna. Mbupmeyan apma vat Kraist Jisasna nj…®vwa kwukiyam…®n. Nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuka m…®na mbang…® Jisas Kraist kat wiyo waavi taagand…®, t…®giyaa nyanat t…®giyam…®n. Nd…®na apma nyaang…®tmba yet…®ga nyanat t…®giyam…®n.  
\v 7 M…®na ngwak walanga kwutaa la wapusepuk kat ke m…®n yelav…®ka. Wan nyaa…®g…®t God kat ngambul…®nja nyaang…®t ana nd…®. God yeta vak kat wutaa God yeta vapmba yet…® m…®la.  
\v 8 Nj…®vwa kwuka m…®na ava m…®na mbang…® tagula vat t…®nd…®, apma vat t…®giyam…®n. M…®na maawut God yet…®ga vak kat n…®ma vat yelav…®ka l…®meyan mbambala apma glei vat t…®giyam…®n. Yelav…®ka yet…®mbandi walaa wowun.  
\v 9 Mbut…®wa nyaang…®t wan nyaang…®t nglaatnd…®. Wan nyaang…®t wutaa ndinyangu ndina maawupmba yelav…®ka yet…®mbandi walaa wowun.  
\v 10 T…®ga l…®ga Godna nj…®vwa n…®mamba kwut…®gan…®n. God n…®n kat v…®ga l…®gand…®. N…®n kat maawut ana t…®v…®l…®gand…®. V…®l…®gan…®n. God ndinyangu yelav…®ka kwutaa la n…®mba kat kwunat…®ga nyana. Nd…® kat maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa la n…®mba kat nd…® God ndi kat kwunat…®gand…®.   
\p
\v 11 Wan m…®n kat mbut…®wa nyaang…®t nat n…®mba kat v…®s…®mogwi m…®la. Wan nyaang…®tmba yet…® ngwula waa awa m…®la.  
\v 12 M…®n kwand…® nyan m…®n. M…®n apma vapmba yet…® m…®la. Kavle vapmba yet…®meyan nat n…®mba m…®n kat waigandi. Nd…® kan mat nyana. Nd…®na maawut yigumba ana s…®ka yelav…®ka l…®gand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga apma nyaang…®t m…®na ambuk. Apma vat m…®na yiga yet…®. Nat n…®mba kat v…®ga woviyaguga al…®. God kat n…®mamba yelav…®ka kwutaa al…®. God wal…®ga vapmba yet…® m…®la. Wungi yet…®ma apma vapmba yet…®meyan Godna mbaapmamba la nat n…®mba v…®ga m…®nai yet…®ga vapmba yet…®giyandi.  
\v 13 Yaweya nandinya kat kawiga kan nj…®vwa kwuka l…®giyam…®n. Ndina n…®nd…®mba laataa God waa apma nyaang…®t ndi kat v…®ga ambuk. Ndi kat m…®na maawupmba yelav…®taa wan apma nyaang…®t ambuk. Ndi kat wan apma nyaang…®t v…®s…®mogwi m…®la.  
\v 14 Tamba Godna yelang…®na n…®ma n…®mba m…®n kat taamba laagaga Godna yelang…®na n…®ma n…®mba m…®n kat taamba laagaga Godna nyaang…®t ngambundi maa Godna nj…®vwa kwupmeya kwondu m…®na tamba klam…®n. Wan vak ke kwagalaga. M…®n yelav…®ka kwutaa wungi vapmba yet…®.  
\v 15 Wan nj…®vwa nj…®mbla nj…®mbla agwup m…®la. Nat vak kat kai waa kwagalaa wan yet…®ma nj…®vwa m…®na agwup m…®la. Nat n…®mba m…®n kat v…®ga waigandi. Apma vat yet…®nda vat lamba n…®ma yigand…® waa waigandi.  
\v 16 Wan yil…®ma vak kat yigumba v…®ga l…®giyam…®n. Nat n…®mba kat v…®s…®mogwil…®ma vat kat yigumba v…®ga l…®giyam…®n. Wan vak m…®n ke kwagalalga. Wan nj…®vwa kwuka yet…®meyan m…®n apma vat yet…®giyam…®n. M…®nai waa nyaang…®t wukiytaa n…®mba apma vapmba yet…®giyandi.   
\c 5  
\s1 GODNA MBAAPMAMBA LA N∆óMBA KAT KWUPMEYA VAT  
\p
\v 1 Av…®t ndu kat ke njska. M…®n yigumba ndina maawut kwunap m…®la. M…®na nyaek vla l…®gandi. Kwand…® nyangu wuna yakwa n…®mba vla l…®gandi waa yelav…®p m…®la.  
\v 2 Av…®t taagwa wuna ny…®me vla l…®gandi waa yelav…®p m…®la. Mwunyawia nyangu wuna nyange vla l…®gandi waa ytelav…®p m…®la. Ndi kat kavle vak ke yelav…®ka yet…®ga.   
\p
\v 3 Ndu kiyandi kwo yet…®ga tolagwa kat m…®n Timoti ndi kat kwunaka k…®g…®nda kwiga v…®ga l…®giyam…®n.  
\v 4 Wat tolagwa nyan yanano l…®leyan l…®la nyangu l…® kat kwanda kwanda kat v…®ga klaga kwigiyandi. Nd…® kat tat ndi kat k…®g…®nda n…®ma sakwat kwil…®l…®. L…® kat l…®g…®mda awat lwinjeya wovuna. Awat kwinjeyan God ndi kat apma vatna yingwa waa waigand…®.  
\v 5 Nat tolagwa l…® kat v…®ga la n…®mba lapman t…®leyan l…® kwo l…®giyal…®. Ngan nandinya God kat yelav…®ka wagala t…®giyal…®.  
\v 6 Wat tolagwa l…®la mbang…® kat m…®na yelav…®ka l…®leyan ana nglaatnd…®. Apma vapmba ana yet…®giyal…®. Apma maawut s…®ka l…®la vak tamba ng…®l…®nd…®.  
\v 7 Kan m…®n kat mbukwa nyaang…®t wundi n…®mba kat ambup m…®la. Mbukwa nyaa…®gn…®tmba yet…®njeyan nat n…®mba ndi kat v…®ga kavle vat yet…®gandi waa ana waigandi.  
\v 8 K…®ta nyan nd…®na yelang…® n…®mba kat kwunatapman yil…®ndeyan wanb nyan wan apma nyaang…®tmba ana yet…®l…®gand…®. Setena yelang…® n…®mbana kavle vak kat nd…® kavle vat yet…®nda vak kwulat…®gand…®.   
\p
\v 9 Tolagwana naambi ndumi kuvut y…®nd…®, l…® kat v…®ga l…®vak l…®lla s…® p…®l…®wuk ngwula. Tak ndu k…®ta klala lat tolagwa kat m…®na ndina s…® p…®l…®wutaa ndi kat kwunaka k…®g…®nda kwiga v…®ga l…®giyam…®n.  
\v 10 K…®ta tolagwa kat wat tolagwa apma vat t…®gal…® waa nat n…®mba wal…®njeyan l…® kat v…®ga l…®giyangwuk. Tamba nyangu kat yigumba v…®ga l…®giyangwuk. Nat n…®mba kat k…®g…®nda kwilaa yigumba kwut…®lan Jisasana mbaapmamba la n…®mbak kwunaka yeta tagwat l…®lleyan awat l…® kat kwunakiyangwuk. Yelogwen kat ta n…®mba kat kwunaka yet…®lat tagwat t…®leyan awat l…® kat kwunakiyangwuk. Wan apma vat yiga yet…®lat taagwa t…®leyan l…® kat v…®ga l…®giyangwuk.  
\v 11-12 Mat nyan tolagwa kat ke v…®ga l…®ngwa. Ndi wandi. Kapma l…®ga nat vak wagalalaa Kraistna nj…®vwa m…®na kwukiyan…®n wandi. Mat nyan tolagwana samat t…®ga wanja nyaang…®k kat kai walaa ndu klavat waigandi. Wanja nyaang…®t kat kai wanjeyan ana nglaand…®. Ndi kat t…®ga ndi kat ke v…®ga l…®ngwa.  
\v 13-14 Mat nyan tolagwa nj…®vwa kwutapman kwo t…®njeyan ana nglaatnd…®. Ndi ngay ngay yilaa mand…®p mand…®p nyaang…®t ngambugiyandi. N…®ma sakwat nyaang…®t ngambugiyandi. Nat nyan tolagwa nat ndu klaigandi wowun ndi kat. Ndu klalaa nyan kwutaa nyan kat v…®ga l…®giyandi. Wupma yil…®njeyan nat n…®mba ndi kat v…®laa Godna mbaapmamba la n…®mba kavle vat yet…®l…®gandi waa ana ndi kat waigandi.  
\v 15 Nat tolagwa kan kavle vat kan mbambala yil…®gandi. Ndi Setena vapmba yel…®gandi.  
\v 16 Nan tolagwanda k…®ta mbaapmamba la taagwa Jisasna mbaapmamba l…®njeyan tolagwa kat k…®g…®nda kwigiyal…®. Kwileyan ngwuk Godna mbaapma n…®mba kapma l…®ga tolagwa kat m…®na k…®g…®nda kwigiyangwuk.   
\p
\v 17 Ngwulogiwnala wan apma nyaang…®t mbut…®ga njambwi n…®mba ndi kat n…®mamba sanya agwi ngwula.  
\v 18 Tamba God waa nyaang…®t k…®ngiyand…® p…®l…®wutnda. Yuwi s…®k veimblivak pal…®ngwenga yi yal…®ga bulmakau nd…®na t…®pmi ke sangiga. K…®giyand…® wan yuwina s…®k waa wand…® God. Nat nyaang…®t wand…®. Nj…®vwa kwut…®ga nyan sanya klaigand…® wand…® God waa p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\v 19 K…®ta nyan Jisasna mbaapma n…®mbana njambwi nyan kat kavle nyaang…®t njambwi nyan kat wanjeya vat awuk ngwula.  
\v 20 Ngwula k…®ta nyan kavle vapmba yet…®vat wandeyan nd…® kat kai awa. Nat n…®mbana n…®nd…®mba laataa l…®ga kai awa. Waneya vak wutaa nat n…®mba nd…®nai ya kavle vak ana yigiyandi.  
\v 21 Wan nyaang…®t n…®n kat wawa nyaang…®tna m…®n yiga ndi kat aywa mbukiyam…®n. S…®mblan ke mbuka. Ndi kat aywaa k…®ta vat t…®ndi, ambuk. Yiliya vat God, Kraist Jisas, Godna apma ensel m…®n kat aywaa wan yiliya vat v…®l…®gandi. Wungi kat t…®ga wawa nyaang…®tmba ambup m…®la.   
\p
\v 22 Kwo n…®mba kat ndi kat taamba laagalaa ke waa Godna nj…®vwa agwut waa ke waa. Tat kwo n…®mba kat ndi kat av…®. Apma n…®mbandi? E? Kavle n…®mbandi? Waa av…®. Wam…®n maa kavle nj…®vwa kwutnjeyan wan kavle vak m…®na lak yigiyand…®. M…®no n…®mbun apma vak m…®na yet…® m…®la.  
\v 23 M…®na yapmba yelogwen t…®gand…® waa wandi, wutwun. Wungi kat t…®ga ngu m…®na ke k…®ga. N…®ma ngu kuvuk ag…®mba. Wan n…®ma ngu m…®na yak kwunatnd…® maa n…®ma sakwat njamb…® ana yelogwen kat t…®giyam…®n.  
\v 24 Nat n…®mba kavle vak yiga yet…®l…®nja vak kat nat n…®mba ana v…®l…®gandi. Ng…®ni kak kiyand…® mala God v…®laa s…®giyand…®.  
\v 25 Nat n…®mba apma vat yiga yet…®l…®nja vat kat nat n…®mba aywaa v…®l…®gandi. Nat n…®mba apma vat yiga yet…®l…®nja vak kat nat n…®mba ana v…®l…®gandi. Ng…®ni kak kiyand…® mala v…®giyandi aywaa.   
\c 6  
\s1 SANYA KLALAPMAN KWO NJ∆óVWA KWUT∆óGA N∆óMBANA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 1 Sanya klalapman kwo nj…®vwa kwut…®ga Jisasna mbaapmamba l…®ga n…®mba ndina njambwi nyan kat ndina maawupmba yelav…®kiyandi. Nd…® apma nyana waa nd…®na s…® kwusoga waigandi. Wungi vat mba yet…®lapman yinjeyan nat n…®mba kwo l…®ga n…®mba ndi kat v…®laa yelav…®kiyandi. Ndi kavle vapmba yet…®l…®gandi. Ndina njambwi nyan God ndi kat kavle vat s…®mogwil…®gand…® waa yelav…®kiyandi.  
\v 2 Sanya klalapman nj…®vwa kwut…®ga Jisasna mbaapmamba l…®ga n…®mba ndina njambwi nyan Jisasna mbaapmamba l…®ga n…®mba ndina njambwi nyan Jisasna mbaapmamba k…®ta vat t…®ndeyan nca kat wupma ana yelav…®kiyandi. Nd…® n…®na k…®ta mbaapma nyan. Nd…®nai waigaa nyaang…®t ana wukiyan…®n waa ana yelav…®kiyandi. Kapma vak yelav…®k ngwula. Ndina njambwi nyan Jisasna mbaapmamba k…®ta vat t…®ndeyan nd…®nai waigaa nj…®vwa apma vat kwukiyandi. Nd…® n…®na k…®ta mbaapma nyana. Ngi kat t…®ga nd…® kat kwunaka woviyaguga l…®gan…®n waa yelav…®taa nd…®na nj…®vwa apma vat kwukiyandi. M…®n ndi kat ambup m…®la wan vak.   
\s1 APMA VAT KLANEYA VAT  
\p
\v 3 Nat n…®mba yandi maa mand…®t kavle nyaang…®t mbut…®gandi. N…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraist waa nyaang…®k kat kai walaa mand…®t kavle nyaang…®t mbut…®gandi. God yeta vak kat kwagalalaa mand…®t kavle nyaang…®t mbutigandi.  
\v 4 Ndi wundi n…®mba yelav…®t…®gandi. Wun apma vat m…®na yet…®l…®gowun waa yelav…®t…®gandi. Wupma waa n…®mba ndina maawut apma vat yelav…®t…®gandi. Ndi ngambul…®njeyan n…®ma sakwat kavle vat m…®na l…®giyand…®. T…®pmigwula yiga yet…®l…®nja vat t…®giyand…®. Wan waleavat yet…®l…®nja vatno ngil…®ga. Nat n…®mbana s…® viyesanda wal…®nja vatno ngil…®ga.  
\v 5 Wundi n…®mba apma maawut ana yelav…®ka yet…®l…®gandi. Wan apma nyaang…®k kat kai walaa ndi ndina maawupmba yelav…®ka waleavat m…®na kwutaa l…®gandi. Wupma yelav…®t…®gandi. God waiga vapmba yet…®neyan kan k…®pmana kwanda kwanda nda aywaa klaigan…®n waa yelav…®t…®gandi. Wupma yelav…®t…®nja nyaang…®t ana nglaatnd…®.  
\v 6 Kan k…®pmana kwanda kwanda nda kat yelav…®tapman God waiga vapmba yetineyan God n…®n kat apma nglei vat kwigiyand…®. Kwindeya nda k…®pmana kwanda kwanda ana nd…®.  
\v 7 N…®n kat name kwukna nandinya kwanda kwanda ndo kwutaa ana yan…®n. Wundumba yineya nj…®bla nd…®no wupma. Kwanda kwanda nda kwutaa ana yigiyan…®n.  
\v 8 N…®na k…®g…®nda n…®na waavwi t…®ndeyan ngiyambak. Nat kwanda kwanda nda kat n…®n ana yelav…®ka yet…®giyan…®n.  
\v 9 K…®ta nyan n…®ma sakwat nda klavat nd…®na maawupmba yelav…®ka yet…®l…®ndeyan wan nyan nd…® mbak waangu veig…®t…®ka ndaiya vap vla kavle yilaa t…®gand…®. Ndinyangu ndino wupma. K…®pmana kwanda kwanda nda kat klavak yelav…®ka yiga kavle yilaa l…®gandi. K…®pmana nda kat klavat yelav…®ka l…®njeyan kavle vat yelav…®ka kavle savle yet…®giyandi.  
\v 10 Sanya klavat maawupmba n…®mamba yelav…®tnjeya vat wan kavle vatna angwa vatna. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba wan kavle vak kat klavak n…®mamba yelav…®ka apma nyaang…®k kat kai waa yet…®ndi. Ndina maawut ng…®ni ana nolin ngwand…®giyandi. Kavle vat ndi kat n…®ma vat yaat…®gand…® apma vat klavak kat.   
\s1 WAN APMA VAK KAT N∆óMAMBA KWUTAA AL∆ó NGWULA  
\p
\v 11 M…®n Timoti Godna nyan m…®n. Wan kavle vat yil…®ga n…®mbana kwupmba ke yiga. M…®n mand…®p vak yiga yet…®. M…®n apma vat kwo yet…®. M…®n God yet…®l…®ga vak vla yet…®. Wan apma nyaang…®k kat nsmamba kwutaa al…® m…®la. Nat n…®mba kat miwa yiga kwunaka woviyaguga al…®. Wan apma vat ke kwagalama. Nat n…®mba kat n…®ma vat ke yiga.  
\v 12 M…®n kwulak kwulapmba yil…®ga nyan vla l…®gam…®n. M…®n kavle vak kwagalalaa ngi apma vapmba kwutaa yet…®giyam…®n. M…®n God n…®ma sakwat n…®mbana n…®nd…®mba laataa wun kat yeta vapmba yet…®gowun waa wam…®n. Wan n…®ma sakwat yisolaa la n…®mba m…®n kat aywaa v…®ga wutndi wana vak. Walaa nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat yet…®meya vat m…®n Godnanamba tamba klam…®n. Wan yet…®vat wama vak at ke kwagalama.  
\v 13-14 M…®n kat wowun, wawa nyaang…®tmba m…®n kwutaa yet…®. Wan m…®n kat wawa nyaang…®t ke kwagalaga. Mand…®t vak m…®n ke yiga. M…®n wan m…®n kat mbukwa nyaang…®t kwutaa nj…®mbla nj…®mbla t…®m…®n mala njambwi nyan Jisas Kraist yaigand…®. Godnagwio Jisaso nyaet nyano kwutaa yet…®meya vak kat m…®n kat v…®ga l…®giyamb…®t. Yelav…®k m…®n. God kwanda kwanda aywaa kwutnd…®, yuvut yil…®gandi. Kraist Jisas Pontias Pailat kat v…®laa wun Godna nyan wun waa nd…® kat v…®s…®mogwind…®. M…®n yelav…®p m…®la. Wan n…®ma nyan mb…®t m…®n kat v…®ga l…®gamb…®t. Ng…®ni Jisas Kraist yaigand…®.  
\v 15 God nd…®na maawupmba yelav…®taa wand…® maa Kraist yaigand…®. God njambwi nyana. Nd…® wan k…®pmana kingna njambwi nyana. Wan k…®pmana njambwi n…®mbana njambwi nyana.  
\v 16 Ndi wan n…®mba aywaa wundumbu yigyandi. Nd…® God kwo l…®giyand…®. Nd…® n…®ma ngleimba kemba l…®ga kavamba yet…®l…®gand…®. Ndinyangu wan kava ana wuleiga nd…® kat v…®giyandi. K…®ta nyan God kat ana v…®l…®gand…®. K…®ta nyan ana al…®ps…®ga God kat v…®giyand…® nd…®na m…®nimba. Godna s…® kwutaa kwusovak kat waigan…®n. Nj…®mbla nj…®mbla nd…® v…®ga l…®giyand…®. Apma vatna.   
\s1 N∆óMA SAKWAT NDO L∆óGA N∆óMBANA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 17 Wan n…®ma sakwat ndo l…®ga n…®mba kat awa m…®la. N…®n n…®ma n…®mba n…®n waa ke yelav…®kngwa waa ndi kat awa m…®la. Ngwutna kwanda kwanda kat n…®mamba ke yelav…®ka l…®ngwa waa awa m…®la. Kwanda kwanda nda ng…®ni ng…®l…®giyand…®. God kat n…®mamba yelav…®ka t…®giyangwuk waa awa m…®la. God n…®n kat apma nda m…®na t…®giyangwuk waa awa m…®la. God n…®n kat apma nda m…®na aywaa kwind…®. Nd…® kat solat s…®ga nolin ngwand…®ga l…®neya nda n…®n kat kwind…®.  
\v 18 Ndi kat awa m…®la. Apma nj…®vwa n…®ma sakwapmba agwut ngwula waa ndi kat ambuk. Kwanda kwanda nat n…®mba kat kwiga waavi nambwiya n…®mba al…® ngwula waa ndi kat ambuk.  
\v 19 Wungi vapmba yet…®njeyan ng…®ni yaiga nandinya ndi kat apma nda ng…®ni t…®giyand…®. Nj…®mbla nj…®mbla ng…®ni t…®njeyan nj…®mbla apma vapmba yet…®giyandi.   
\s1 KWUPMEYA NJ∆óMBLA NJ∆óMBLA NG∆óNI T∆óNJEYAN  
\p
\v 20 Timoti m…®n kat kwinja nj…®vwa m…®n yigumba kwunaka kwutaa yet…®mba. Nat n…®mba god waa nyaang…®t kwagalalaa ndi ndina maawupmba yelav…®tnja vapmba ngambuga yet…®l…®gandi. N…®na maawupmba l…®ga vak apma vatna waa wal…®gandi. Ndinai kwuta yet…®ga vat apma vat ana nd…®. M…®n ndi kat kwaglala m…®la.  
\v 21 Wan kavle nyaang…®t kwutaa yet…®l…®ga n…®mba God waa apma nyaang…®k kat maawut t…®v…®ga yet…®l…®gandi. God awagapma m…®n kat kwunatndangat wowun.   